kw.name: Run Accessibility Tests
kw.doc: Executes accessibility tests in current page by injecting axe-core javascript and write results into `result_file` (json). Return result statisitics

kw.name: Log
kw.doc: Logs the given message with the given level.

kw.name: Set Global Variable
kw.doc: Makes a variable available globally in all tests and suites.

kw.name: Log Readable Accessibility Result
kw.doc: Inserts readable accessibility result into `log.html` based on given `type`. Need to be used after `Run Accessibility Tests` keyword
